page.title: 20WARDOUR CREDITS
page.content:
The children of Wardour Primary school,in the Upper Junior Class, have prepared this Domesday Project Disk in June 1985.Here are the names of the children who took part......

Mrs McGrail helped us with mapping and computerwork.The people of the whole Wardour Domesday area have been very helpful by giving us lots of useful information. Mr and Mrs Richardson got us started.
